                                    <mutableString key="text">Last Updated:
Jan 01, 2026
Welcome to the Qadsia mobile application and website (“App” and “Site”). These Terms &amp; Conditions (“Terms”) govern your use of the App and Site, operated by Qadsia SC (“we,” “us,” “our”). By accessing or using the App or Site, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree with any part of these Terms, you must stop using the App and Site immediately.
1. Acceptance of Terms
By registering, accessing, or using the Qadsia App or Site, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be legally bound by these Terms, including any updates or modifications that we may make from time to time.
2. Changes to Terms
We reserve the right to update, modify, or replace any part of these Terms at any time without prior notice. Revised Terms will be effective immediately when posted. Your continued use of the App or Site after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the new Terms.
3. Eligibility
You represent that you are at least 16 years old or have parental/guardian consent to use the App and Site. If you are under 18 years of age, you may use the App and Site only with involvement of a parent or guardian.
4. User Accounts
To access certain features (such as ticket purchases, profile, or loyalty points), you may be required to register and create an account.
You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information when creating your account.
You are responsible for safeguarding your account login details and for all activities that occur under your account.
5. Acceptable Use
You agree not to use the App or Site:
In any way that violates any applicable law, regulation, or these Terms;
To engage in harmful, abusive, defamatory, or offensive conduct;
To upload or share content that infringes the rights of others, including intellectual property rights; or
To interfere with or disrupt the App’s functionality.
6. Intellectual Property
All content on the App and Site — including text, graphics, logos, images, audio, and software — is the property of Qadsia SC or its licensors and is protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws. You may not copy, distribute, or create derivative works from this content without express permission.
7. Purchases and Payments
If the App or Site allows purchases (e.g., tickets, merchandise), you agree to:
Provide accurate payment information;
Comply with the terms of any third-party payment processors;
Pay any applicable taxes, fees, or charges.
All purchases are final unless otherwise stated in a specific refund policy.
8. Limitation of Liability
To the maximum extent permitted by law:
Qadsia SC and its affiliates shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the App or Site;
Your use of the App and Site is at your sole risk.
9. Disclaimers
The App and Site are provided on an “AS IS” and “AS AVAILABLE” basis. Qadsia SC makes no warranties of any kind, whether express or implied, regarding the operation of the App or Site or the content therein.
10. Governing Law
These Terms will be governed by and interpreted in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction where Qadsia SC is registered, without regard to its conflict of law principles.
11. Termination
We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to the App or Site at any time for any reason, including if you violate these Terms.
12. Contact Information
If you have questions about these Terms &amp; Conditions, you can contact us at:
📩 Email: Info@Qadsia.com</mutableString>
